{"parse":{"title":"Sholay: The Making of a Classic","pageid":34357366,"revid":841507384,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox vcard\" style=\"width:22em\"><caption style=\"font-style:italic;padding-bottom:0.2em;\">Sholay: The Making of a Classic <span class=\"Z3988\" title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Sholay%3A+The+Making+of+a+Classic&amp;rft.author=%5B%5BAnupama+Chopra%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=December+2000&amp;rft.pub=Penguin+Books+India&amp;rft.pages=194\"></span></caption><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;display:none\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Author</th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Anupama_Chopra\" title=\"Anupama Chopra\">Anupama Chopra</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Country</th><td>\nIndia</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Language</th><td>\nEnglish</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Subject</th><td>\nFilm</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Publisher</th><td>\nPenguin Books India</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><div style=\"padding:0.1em 0;line-height:1.2em;\">Publication date</div></th><td>\nDecember 2000</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Media&#160;type</th><td>\nPrint</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Pages</th><td>\n194</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Awards</th><td>\n'Best Book On Film' Year 2000</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a></th><td>\n<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/014029970X\" title=\"Special:BookSources/014029970X\">014029970X</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><i><b>Sholay: The Making of a Classic</b></i> is a 2000 book written by <a href=\"/wiki/Anupama_Chopra\" title=\"Anupama Chopra\">Anupama Chopra</a> on a Bollywood classic <i><a href=\"/wiki/Sholay\" title=\"Sholay\">Sholay</a></i> (1975).<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The book was released in 2000 by Penguin Books India.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The book is based on the making of the film shooting.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The book initially sold 10,000 copies,<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and won the 2001 <a href=\"/wiki/National_Film_Award_for_Best_Book_on_Cinema\" title=\"National Film Award for Best Book on Cinema\">National Film Award for Best Book on Cinema</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-48thawardPDF_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-48thawardPDF-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Content\">Content</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Sholay:_The_Making_of_a_Classic&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Content\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The book is an inside look at the film's production, based on interviews with the director, stars, and crew members.<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Sholay:_The_Making_of_a_Classic&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ibnlive.i